			<div class="content" id="post-content-1664755">
									

<p>This is it, really. This covers everything people would need to know for merchandise as well. At least the part of it that would have anything to do with us. If they follow the rules of CC, then whether or not they sell what they make is irrelevant, and we detail the rules of CC here well enough that people could go off of this guide alone. The only other thing there would be to say is &quot;if you decide to sell merchandise based off of SCP materials then we STRONGLY encourage you to make sure that the original authors of the material you reference are ok with you doing so, so that we don't end up with a bunch of angry authors who decide to delete their stuff and leave.&quot;</p>
<p>If you mean merchandise as in how it would work on the official site if we ever chose to have a store(which we may or may not, we are completely undecided on that), we'll write that bridge when we come to it.</p>

